âœ… 10 phases techniques (version propre et production-ready)
Add a new VMDK to the VM (2â€“4 GiB, dedicated for /boot)
Detect the new disk at OS level (lsblk, identify /dev/sdb)
Create the partition table on the new disk (MBR for BIOS, GPT for UEFI)
Create the /boot partition (and /boot/efi if UEFI)
