Mount the new disk temporarily and copy /boot content (rsync)
Chroot on the new /boot and reinstall GRUB on the new disk
Update /etc/fstab to mount /boot from the new disk (keep old /boot commented for rollback)
Validate mounts and boot configuration before reboot
Reboot the VM and validate successful boot and kernel loading
